@feature macro recorder
  # record user actions and create a macro for testing purposes.
  # the macro recorder is a singleton, so it can be accessed from anywhere.
  # the macro recorder is started by calling the start method.
  # the macro recorder is stopped by calling the stop method.
  # the macro recorder is reset by calling the reset method.
  # the macro recorder is saved by calling the save method.
  # the macro recorder is loaded by calling the load method.
